Uruk-hai Horde<br />
Uruk Assault Band<br />
Lindenroot<br />
Legolas, Dauntless Hunter<br />
<br />
These are only modification cards. The common Treebeard obviously doesn&#39;t do much, but the rare one fits in perfectly with this deck. I would say that these cards should be the first ones out:<br />
<br />
Warmed up a Bit<br />
Treebeard, Oldest Living Thing<br />
All Gondor cards if you put in Legolas, DH<br />
Severed His Bonds x2<br />
Uruk-hai Mob<br />
Attack on Helm&#39;s Deep x1<br />
Uruk-hai Marauder x1<br />
<br />
Any tips on how to improve this deck with commons or uncommons would be great.<br />
<br />
To those seeing this in the future: Remember that this is pre-EoF, so please don&#39;t take ratings off because it doesn&#39;t have a card from EoF.<br />
